ActImmigration and Refugee Protection Act
SubjectRegulations Amending the Immigration and Refugee Protection Regulations (Miscellaneous Program)
PrecisTo ensure consistency between the English and French versions of the text, to amend language where more appropriate and/or more precise language was deemed necessary by the Standing Joint Committee for the Scrutiny of Regulations, to harmonize two related provisions relating to the requirement of fees for services rendered, and to replace the incorrect reference to the Financial Administration Act as an enabling authority and replace it with the Immigration and Refugee Protection Act.
RegistrationRegistration: SOR/ 2009-0163 Publication Date: 2009-06-24
